org.jpy

Class PyDictWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jpy.PyDictWrapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoCloseable, Map<PyObject,PyObject>

    public class PyDictWrapper
extends Object
implements Map<PyObject,PyObject>, AutoCloseable
    A simple wrapper around PyObjects that are actually Python dictionaries, to present the most useful parts of a Map interface.
